data.description: The #1 builder in the country, D.R. Horton, has just opened up their newest community, Sims Landing! This home is located between Fort Gordon's Gate 1 & 2 and minutes to highways, shopping, and restaurants. The Packard floor plan has 4 bedrooms & 2.5 baths with 9ft ceilings on the first floor as luxury vinyl tile plank in kitchen area, breakfast and family room. The kitchen includes granite countertops, 30" cabinets with rope crown molding detail, tile backsplash and much more. Outside of the home is a fully sodded yard with a 2 zone sprinkler system. Estimated completion date: 12/2017. **All photos are stock photos and may be of like home and may not reflect list price**
